    • leftFrontDirection

      public com.qualcomm.robotcore.hardware.DcMotorSimple.Direction leftFrontDirection
      Direction motor spins when positive power is applied - to drive the motor "backwards", do not set this to reverse! Set the power to a negative value. What "FORWARD" or "REVERSE" is depends on your motors and how you've laid out your robot, so determine that experimentally.
